headline: Madison Covered Call & Equity Income Fund Q1 2025 Investment Strategy Letter
summary: Over the full quarter, the S&P 500 lost 4.3% while the CBOE S&P 500 Buy-Write Index fell 3.1%. The Fund (class Y) outperformed both benchmarks, posting a 1.9% decline.
